\c 22
\nb
\v 1 UDavida wasesithi: Le yindlu yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu, laleli lilathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa kaIsrayeli\x + 21.18,19,26,28. 2 Lan. 3.1. Dute. 12.5.\x*.
\s UDavida ulungiselela ukwakhiwa kwethempeli
\p
\v 2 UDavida waselaya ukubuthanisa abezizweni ababeselizweni lakoIsrayeli\x + 1 Kho. 9.21. 2 Lan. 2.17.\x*; wamisa ababazi bamatshe ukuthi babaze amatshe alungisiweyo okwakha indlu kaNkulunkulu\x + 1 Kho. 5.17.\x*.
\v 3 UDavida waselungisa insimbi enengi kakhulu yezipikili zezivalo zamasango leyokuhlanganisa\x + 2 Lan. 34.11.\x*; lethusi elinengi kakhulu elalingela\add kulinganiswa nge\add*sisindo\x + 22.14. 1 Kho. 7.47.\x*;
\v 4 lezigodo zemisedari ezingelakubalwa; ngoba amaSidoni lamaTire amlethela uDavida izigodo zemisedari ezinengi kakhulu\x + 1 Kho. 5.6.\x*.
\v 5 UDavida wasesithi: USolomoni indodana yami ungumfana, ubuthakathaka, lendlu ezakwakhelwa iN\nd kosi\nd* kumele yenziwe ibe nkulu kakhulu, ibe lebizo ibe lodumo emazweni wonke. Ngakho ngizayilungiselela. UDavida waselungiselela kakhulu phambi kokufa kwakhe\x + 29.1. 1 Kho. 3.7. Zaga 4.3.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Wasebiza uSolomoni indodana yakhe, wamlaya ukuthi akhele iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli indlu.
\v 7 UDavida wasesithi kuSolomoni: Ndodana yami, mina-ke, kwakusenhliziyweni yami\x + 2 Lan. 24.4. 29.10. 2 Sam. 7.3. Hlab. 132.1-5.\x* ukwakhela ibizo leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wami indlu\x + 22.8,19. Dute. 12.5,11. 1 Kho. 5.3.\x*.
\v 8 Kodwa ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lafika kimi lisithi: Uchithe igazi elinengi\x + 28.3.\x*, walawula izimpi ezinkulu; kawuyikwakhela ibizo lami indlu, ngoba uchithe igazi elinengi emhlabeni phambi kwami\x + 1 Kho. 5.3.\x*.
\v 9 Khangela, uzazalelwa indodana ezakuba ngumuntu wokuphumula\x + 22.18. 1 Kho. 4.25. 5.4.\x*; njalo ngizayiphumuza ezitheni zayo zonke inhlangothi zonke: Ngoba ibizo layo lizakuba nguSolomoni, njalo ngizanika ukuthula lokuphumula phezu kukaIsrayeli ensukwini zakhe.
\v 10 Yena uzakwakhela ibizo lami indlu\x + 2 Sam. 7.13.\x*. Yena-ke uzakuba yindodana yami, lami ngibe nguyise; ngiqinise isihlalo sakhe sobukhosi phezu kukaIsrayeli kuze kube nininini\x + 28.6. 2 Sam. 7.14. Heb. 1.5.\x*.
\v 11 Khathesi, ndodana yami, iN\nd kosi\nd* ibe lawe, njalo uphumelele wakhe indlu yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, njengokutsho kwayo ngawe\x + 22.16. 1 Sam. 20.13.\x*.
\v 12 Kuphela iN\nd kosi\nd* ikunike inhlakanipho lokuqedisisa, ikulaye ngoIsrayeli, ukuze ulondoloze umlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 1 Kho. 3.9,12. Hlab. 72.1.\x*.
\v 13 Khona uzaphumelela, uba unanzelela ukwenza izimiso lezahlulelo iN\nd kosi\nd* eyakulaya uMozisi ngoIsrayeli\x + 28.7. Josh. 1.7,8.\x*; qina, ube lesibindi\x + 28.20. Dute. 31.6.\x*; ungesabi, ungatshaywa luvalo\x + Dute. 31.8.\x*.
\v 14 Khangela-ke, ekuhluphekeni kwami ngilungisele indlu yeN\nd kosi\nd* \w amathalenta\w** egolide ayizinkulungwane ezilikhulu, lamathalenta esiliva ayizinkulungwane eziyinkulungwane\x + 29.4.\x*, lethusi lensimbi okungela\add kulinganiswa nge\add*sisindo\x + 22.3.\x*, ngoba kunengi kakhulu; ngilungise lezigodo lamatshe. Uzakwengezelela-ke kukho.
\v 15 Njalo ulezisebenzi ezinengi, ababazi bamatshe, lezingcitshi zamatshe lezezigodo, layo yonke indoda ehlakaniphileyo kuwo wonke umsebenzi.
\v 16 Kakulanani legolide, lelesiliva, lelethusi, lelensimbi\x + 22.4.\x*. Sukuma usebenze; njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* ibe lawe\x + 22.11.\x*!
\p
\v 17 UDavida waselaya zonke izinduna zakoIsrayeli ukusiza uSolomoni indodana yakhe\x + 28.1,2.\x*, \add esithi\add*:
\v 18 IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu kayilani yini\x + Jobe 3.11.\x*? Kambe \add ka\add*yilinik\add anga\add* yini ukuphumula inhlangothi zonke\x + 23.25. 22.9. Dute. 12.10. Josh. 21.44. 23.1. 2 Sam. 7.1.\x*? Ngoba inikele abahlali belizwe esandleni sami, lelizwe lehliselwe phansi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* laphambi kwabantu bayo.
\v 19 Khathesi misani inhliziyo yenu lomphefumulo wenu ukudinga iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + 2 Lan. 20.3.\x*. Sukumani-ke lakhe indawo engcwele yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu, ukungenisa umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* lezitsha ezingcwele zikaNkulunkulu endlini eyakhelwe ibizo leN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 1 Kho. 8.6,21. 2 Lan. 5.7. 6.11.\x*.